name: SugarDaddyForMe
overview:
SugarDaddyForMe.com is an online dating website where successful men and attractive women can meet for mutually pleasing and very honest relationships.

Recently there has been a huge trend towards a specific kind of no-nonsense, no strings dating website gaining immense popularity on the Internet. This hot new trend is online dating websites for Sugar Daddies and Sugar Babies, and SugarDaddyForMe.com is the largest online dating website of its kind in the world, double the size of any other competitor.

The dating site currently has over 4 million members, with over 2,000 new sugar daddy and sugar baby profiles every day and 1.5 million unique new visitors every month.

SugarDaddyForMe.com has been featured on two full episodes of both the Montel Williams Show and on the Tyra Banks Show. We were recently featured on MTV True Life- “I’m a Sugar Baby”. We have also been featured in stories on Good Morning America as well as on their website and on FoxNews.com.
